# ğŸ“š ExamPro - Online Assessment Platform

> **âš ï¸ PROJECT STATUS: PHASE 1 COMPLETED - IN ACTIVE DEVELOPMENT**
> 
> This project is currently in its **first phase of development**. Core functionalities (user authentication, test creation, and test taking) have been successfully implemented. Advanced features like analytics, performance tracking, and test management are planned for future releases.

A full-stack web application for creating, managing, and taking online MCQ assessments. Built with Spring Boot backend and vanilla JavaScript frontend.

