## ğŸ¯ Project Overview

**ExamPro** is an online assessment system that enables educators to create custom multiple-choice question (MCQ) tests, schedule them, and share them with students. Students can take tests within a time limit and receive instant results with detailed answer reviews.

### ğŸš€ Development Phases

#### âœ… Phase 1 - COMPLETED (Current Release)

The following **core functionalities** have been fully implemented and tested:

##### ğŸ” **Authentication System**
- âœ… User registration with email verification
- âœ… Secure password validation (8+ characters, uppercase, lowercase, number, special character)
- âœ… Email verification via OTP (6-digit code sent to Gmail)
- âœ… Professional HTML email templates with branding
- âœ… Login/Logout functionality
- âœ… Session management with localStorage

##### ğŸ“ **Test Creation**
- âœ… Create custom MCQ tests with unlimited questions
- âœ… Set test duration (in minutes)
- âœ… Schedule test activation date and time
- âœ… Add 4-option multiple choice questions
- âœ… Mark correct answers for each question
- âœ… Preview test before publishing
- âœ… Save tests as drafts (localStorage)
- âœ… Generate unique shareable 8-character test codes
- âœ… Copy test code and share link functionality

##### âœï¸ **Test Taking**
- âœ… Access test via unique code
- âœ… Student information collection (name & email)
- âœ… Timer-based test sessions with visual countdown
- âœ… Color-coded timer warnings (orange at 5 min, red at 1 min)
- âœ… Navigate between questions (Previous/Next buttons)
- âœ… Review and change answers before submission
- âœ… Auto-submit when time expires
- âœ… Prevent duplicate test attempts (one attempt per student per test)
- âœ… Progress indicator showing current question number

##### ğŸ“Š **Results & Review**
- âœ… Instant score calculation upon submission
- âœ… Percentage-based performance rating
- âœ… Detailed answer review with correct/incorrect highlighting
- âœ… Question-by-question breakdown
- âœ… Display student's selected answer vs correct answer
- âœ… Performance messages based on score ranges
- âœ… Visual feedback with color-coded results (green for correct, red for incorrect)

