                         â”‚ selected_answer     â”‚
                         â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜
```

### Detailed Tables

#### ğŸ“‹ `users` Table
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|-------------|
| id | BIGINT | PRIMARY KEY, AUTO_INCREMENT | Unique user identifier |
| name | VARCHAR(255) | NOT NULL | User's full name |
| email | VARCHAR(255) | UNIQUE, NOT NULL | User's email address |
| password | VARCHAR(255) | NOT NULL | BCrypt hashed password |
| verified | BOOLEAN | DEFAULT FALSE | Email verification status |
| verification_code | VARCHAR(6) | NULLABLE | 6-digit OTP code |

**Sample Data:**
```sql
INSERT INTO users VALUES (1, 'John Doe', 'john@example.com', '$2a$10$...', true, NULL);
```

#### ğŸ“ `tests` Table
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|-------------|
| id | BIGINT | PRIMARY KEY, AUTO_INCREMENT | Unique test identifier |
| title | VARCHAR(255) | NOT NULL | Test title/name |
| duration | INT | NOT NULL | Duration in minutes |
| description | TEXT | NULLABLE | Test description |
| activation_date_time | DATETIME | NOT NULL | When test becomes available |
| test_code | VARCHAR(8) | UNIQUE, NOT NULL | Shareable test code |
| created_by | VARCHAR(255) | NOT NULL | Creator's email (FK to users) |
| created_at | DATETIME | DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP | Creation timestamp |
| status | VARCHAR(50) | DEFAULT 'scheduled' | Test status |

**Sample Data:**
```sql
INSERT INTO tests VALUES (1, 'Math Quiz', 30, 'Chapter 1', '2026-02-10 14:00:00', 'ABC12XYZ', 'john@example.com', NOW(), 'active');
```

#### â“ `questions` Table
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|-------------|
| id | BIGINT | PRIMARY KEY, AUTO_INCREMENT | Unique question identifier |
| test_id | BIGINT | FOREIGN KEY â†’ tests(id) | Reference to parent test |
| question_text | TEXT | NOT NULL | The question |
| option_a | VARCHAR(500) | NOT NULL | Option A |
| option_b | VARCHAR(500) | NOT NULL | Option B |
| option_c | VARCHAR(500) | NOT NULL | Option C |
| option_d | VARCHAR(500) | NOT NULL | Option D |
| correct_answer | INT | NOT NULL (0-3) | Correct option index (0=A, 1=B, 2=C, 3=D) |

**Sample Data:**
```sql
INSERT INTO questions VALUES (1, 1, 'What is 2+2?', '3', '4', '5', '6', 1);
```

#### ğŸ“Š `test_results` Table
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|-------------|
| id | BIGINT | PRIMARY KEY, AUTO_INCREMENT | Unique result identifier |
| test_id | BIGINT | FOREIGN KEY â†’ tests(id) | Reference to test taken |
| student_email | VARCHAR(255) | NOT NULL | Student's email |
| student_name | VARCHAR(255) | NOT NULL | Student's name |
| score | INT | NOT NULL | Number of correct answers |
| total_questions | INT | NOT NULL | Total questions in test |
| submitted_at | DATETIME | DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP | Submission time |

**Sample Data:**
```sql
INSERT INTO test_results VALUES (1, 1, 'alice@example.com', 'Alice Smith', 8, 10, NOW());
```

#### âœ… `student_answers` Table
| Column | Type | Constraints | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|-------------|
| result_id | BIGINT | FOREIGN KEY â†’ test_results(id) | Reference to result |
| question_id | BIGINT | NOT NULL | Question ID |
| selected_answer | INT | NOT NULL (0-3) | Selected option (0=A, 1=B, 2=C, 3=D) |

**Sample Data:**
```sql
INSERT INTO student_answers VALUES (1, 1, 1);  -- Answered B for question 1
```

